She wears a fitted ribbed white tank top and loose white linen shorts with an elastic waistband. A large brown designer shoulder bag with repeating pattern rests on her left arm. Her posture is relaxed, right arm resting on a glass safety barrier, left arm by her side. The city below is packed with mid- and high-rise buildings stretching into hazy distance, with visible structures including cylindrical rooftops and modern towers. Lighting is direct and high-angled, casting sharp highlights and minimal shadows on her skin and clothing. The sky is pale and overexposed, and distant buildings appear desaturated due to heat haze. Reflections on the glass and floor surfaces are slightly distorted and contrasty, creating a slightly washed-out palette with flattened depth, as if captured by a mobile camera under extreme daylight. The framing is vertical and eye-level, centered on her figure against the panoramic skyline.
